# Input

```yaml
? simple
: value
? valueless
? multiline
  scalar key
: kept
? - seq
  - key
: - seq
  - value
? key # comment
: value
sets: !!set
  ? one
  ? two

```


# Formatted

```yaml
simple: value
valueless:
? multiline
  scalar key
: kept
? - seq
  - key
: - seq
  - value
key: # comment
  value
sets: !!set
  ? one
  ? two

```
